In re Resignation of DeVictor.

[Cite as In re Resignation of DeVictor (1990), 50 Ohio St. 3d 605.]

(No. 90-365 Submitted March 14, 1990 Decided March 28, 1990.)

The resignation of Robert Louis DeVictor as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown -and Resnick, JJ., concur.
